413
00:26:48,940 --> 00:26:50,818
Oh, non ! Continental Accent,

414
00:26:50,985 --> 00:26:51,985
Allez !

415
00:26:56,698 --> 00:26:57,698
Regarde !

416
00:27:01,000 --> 00:27:02,150
Attends, attends...

417
00:27:03,271 --> 00:27:04,471
Vas-y !

418
00:27:26,995 --> 00:27:30,398
