455
00:29:53,027 --> 00:29:54,042
Je serai là.

456
00:29:55,158 --> 00:29:56,158
Merci.

457
00:29:57,389 --> 00:29:59,039
Je le garde en tête.

458
00:30:01,007 --> 00:30:02,307
À plus tard.

459
00:30:04,790 --> 00:30:05,790
Au revoir.

460
